flowchart TD
    Start[PR opened/updated] --> Detect[Reviewer Evidence Detector v4.35]

    Detect --> Q1{Reviewer evidence found?}

    Q1 -->|Yes| Q2{Evidence type?}
    Q1 -->|No| Q3{Reviewer required?}

    Q2 -->|reviewer_comment| Trust1[Trust: comment]
    Q2 -->|reviewer_approval| Trust2[Trust: approval]
    Q2 -->|reviewer_review| Trust3[Trust: review]
    Q2 -->|code_review| Trust4[Trust: code review]

    Trust1 --> Policy[Trust Policy v4.36]
    Trust2 --> Policy
    Trust3 --> Policy
    Trust4 --> Policy

    Q3 -->|HIGH-RISK| Block[Gate BLOCKED]
    Q3 -->|STANDARD| Warn[Warning: no reviewer evidence]
    Q3 -->|FAST| Skip[Skip: not required]
    Q3 -->|DIRECT| Skip

    Policy --> Q4{Trusted?}

    Q4 -->|Yes| Pass[Gate passes reviewer check]
    Q4 -->|No| Block

    Warn --> Pass
    Skip --> Pass
